programme.title: Naam Series S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Kisah enam pemuzik yang sangat berbeza latar belakang bersatu kerana satu impian, untuk menonjol dan membuktikan bakat mereka dalam dunia muzik. Mereka membentuk sebuah kumpulan muzik (band) yang dinamakan One Music. Walau bagaimanapun, jalan menuju impian ini tidak semudah yang disangka.

programme.title: The Gift
programme.desc: Kisah kehidupan masyarakat berbilang kaum yang melibatkan keluarga Matthew, James, Chong, Abu, Ravi dan Chudar di sebuah taman perumahan di Kuala Lumpur. Sempena perayaan Krismas, setiap keluarga mendapat 'hadiah' yang amat bermakna dalam kehidupan mereka!

programme.title: Once Upon A Time In Cyprus S1 Ep20
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang lelaki bernama Yusuf, yang terperangkap dalam konflik yang semakin memuncak antara masyarakat Turki dan Yunani di Cyprus. Ketika ketegangan politik semakin meruncing, Yusuf bersama sahabat-sahabatnya harus membuat pilihan yang sukar antara mempertahankan bangsa dan mencari jalan damai. "Once Upon A Time In Cyprus" bukan hanya menceritakan tentang konflik, tetapi juga tentang kekuatan hubungan manusia, cinta dan pengorbanan dalam menghadapi cabaran yang tidak terduga.

programme.title: Pak Pandir Moden S1 Ep9
programme.desc: Kisah Pak Pandir, seorang lelaki lurus yang mengalami pelbagai masalah akibat dari sifat lurus bendulnya.

programme.title: Berita Mandarin
programme.desc: Ikuti berita berbahasa Mandarin yang memaparkan perkembangan politik, sosial, ekonomi, sukan, hiburan dan isu-isu semasa.

programme.title: Flying High S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Rancangan ini mengisahkan impian seseorang yang ingin bekerja dalam kerjaya yang diminati dapat direalisasikan. Tetapi hanya seorang peserta yang akan dipilih bagi setiap episod dan mereka akan menjalani beberapa ujian sebelum dipilih terima bekerja. Tiga ujian tersebut adalah perubahan imej, sesi latihan bimbingan bersama mentor terpilih dan terakhir adalah ujian.

programme.title: BERITA TAMIL
programme.desc: Berita berbahasa Tamil yang memaparkan perkembangan politik, sosial, ekonomi, sukan, hiburan dan isu-isu semasa.

programme.title: My Dearest S1 Ep14
programme.desc: Kisah percintaan tragis antara seorang bangsawan misteri, Lee Jang-hyun, dan seorang wanita bangsawan berani, Yoo Gil-chae, yang berlaku ketika zaman penjajahan Dinasti Qing di Korea. Dalam suasana perang dan huru-hara, cinta mereka diuji dengan perpisahan, pengorbanan dan penderitaan. Jang-hyun yang menyembunyikan kisah silamnya, mula berubah setelah jatuh cinta dengan Gil-chae. Sementara itu, Gil-chae belajar tentang erti cinta sebenar dan ketabahan melalui liku-liku yang menyayat hati.

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: Empat sahabat dari latar budaya berbeza Amy, Raju, Chen dan Diana menjalin persahabatan yang tidak diduga dengan Jack, seorang pelajar pertukaran dan vlogger yang bersemangat tinggi, semasa mengikuti program MBA di Malaysia. Semangat Jack terhadap kehidupan dan kekagumannya terhadap budaya Malaysia menyatukan mereka ketika mereka menjelajah tempat-tempat ikonik, berkongsi tradisi kulinari, dan menempuh suka duka sepanjang semester bersama.

programme.title: Lethal Weapon S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Apabila Riggs dan Murtaugh menyiasat kematian seorang pakar bedah plastik, mereka ditarik ke dalam kes yang melibatkan kumpulan dadah haram. Keadaan menjadi panas apabila Karen Palmer dari DEA dan Riggs bersaing untuk menyelesaikan kes itu terlebih dahulu. Sementara itu, Trish dan Murtaugh menghadapi cabaran emosi menghantar anak pertama mereka RJ ke kolej.

programme.title: Nam Naatu Arusuvai S1 Ep9
programme.desc: Majalah masakan yang menampilkan Chef Vasantha Jothi mendemonstrasikan cara-cara menyediakan 'bhatura' dengan 'chole' atau 'kacang' dan 'atta halwa' disamping menjelaskan kebaikan masakan dan makanan tradisional tersebut untuk kesihatan.

programme.title: Jerangkap Cinta S1 Ep11
programme.desc: Ikuti kisah tiga sahabat Sofea, Rashid dan Bahar menjalani pelbagai situasi suka dan duka. Rashid dan Bahar menaruh hati kepada Sofea. Tetapi siapakah yang menjadi pilihan Sofea..?

programme.title: Wadi Rahmah S1 Ep20
programme.desc: Kisah konflik sekumpulan anak muda yang menerajui projek ternakan cacing yang dianggap menggelikan. Mereka cuba merubah persepsi masyarakat dan membuka syarikat Wadi Rahmah Industri Sdn Bhd yang mengusahakan projek tersebut.

programme.title: Sambavam S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Drama kemasyarakatan yang memaparkan hubungan kekeluargaan, persahabatan dan percintaan.

programme.title: Manasum Manasum S1 Ep7
programme.desc: Manickam dan keluarganya telah terlibat dalam kemalangan jalan raya di mana isterinya telah meninggal dunia. Manickam telah menghadapi masalah untuk menjaga tiga orang anak-anaknya yang menjadi anak yatim.

programme.title: Perplexed Love S1 Ep11
programme.desc: Memaparkan kisah berkaitan dengan pelbagai isu semasa yang sering berlaku dalam masyarakat.

programme.title: The Gift
programme.desc: Kisah kehidupan masyarakat berbilang kaum yang melibatkan keluarga Matthew, James, Chong, Abu, Ravi dan Chudar di sebuah taman perumahan di Kuala Lumpur. Sempena perayaan Krismas, setiap keluarga mendapat 'hadiah' yang amat bermakna dalam kehidupan mereka!

programme.title: Bara Yang Ku Genggam S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Kehidupan Juwita yang bahagia setelah mendirikan rumahtangga dengan lelaki pilihannya, Adli berubah setelah mereka terlibat dalam kemalangan yang tanpa diduga telah meragut nyawa suaminya itu. Namun Juwita hanya diberitahu kematian suaminya setelah selamat melahirkan anak sulongnya, Aiman. Daripada wanita 'biasa-biasa' yang bergelar suri rumah, Juwita bangkit semula daripada trauma episod sedih kehilangan suaminya kerana sedar dia masih perlu membesarkan Aiman dengan penuh kasih sayang.

programme.title: Fruiterama S1 Ep11

programme.desc: Dzulkarnain telah dianiayai dengan ilmu hitam oleh Manuja menyebabkan dia sakit, namun diselamatkan oleh para pendekar sakti. Dalam pertempuran itu, Jagat mati tetapi Nading dan Lang Kajai dapat melarikan diri. Dzulkarnain yang sebenarnya sudah nazak, akhirnya mati.

programme.title: Motif
programme.desc: Sementara itu, penyiasat Sara dibunuh oleh Madam Kwan yang menyembunyikan rahsia gelap suaminya. Namun Hamdi berjaya melarikan diri dan mendedahkan lokasi sebenar Kasyorga. Rodi, walau cedera, kembali bangkit untuk menyelamatkan Kasyorga. Akhirnya, Vince-anak Madam Kwanmuncul, menandakan konspirasi belum berakhir.

programme.title: Bisikan Syaitan

programme.title: Obsesi Dia EP4 S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Affiyah ditemui cedera parah dan dihantar ke hospital setelah dilanggar dan dipukul oleh Rafeeq. Kejadian yang berlaku disaksikan oleh Razi. Affiyah tersedar namun ingatannya tidak baik

programme.title: Susuk
programme.desc: Soraya, seorang jururawat yang bercita-cita menjadi artis, mula menggunakan ilmu susuk untuk memperoleh kecantikan dan populariti. Namun, apabila dia semakin tenggelam dalam dunia glamour dan ketamakan, susuk itu mula menuntut bayaran yang mengerikan. Di sebalik kilauan dunia hiburan, tersimpan rahsia gelap yang membawa kepada kehancuran diri.

programme.title: Barajiwa EP6 S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Noramina kagum dengan kemahiran bertarung Uzair dan menawar pekerjaan sebagai pengawal peribadinya. Uzair kini mempunyai pekerjaan yang sesuai dan boleh menyewa tempat tinggal sendiri. Hatta mula sedar ada sesuatu yang baik dan istimewa pada Uzair. Uzair mula mesra dengan Noramina.

programme.desc: Hariz, seorang novelis terkenal mendapati kekasihnya curang. Andy sahabat baiknya, selamatkan Hariz dengan membawanya ke pekan yang kecil sehingga Amelia muncul di perkampungan tersebut kerana tunangnya dijumpai lemas.

programme.title: Kutuk
programme.desc: Maya, seorang jururawat yang baru berpindah ke sebuah asrama lama di pinggir bandar, mula diganggu oleh kejadian aneh dan menyeramkan. Dia kemudian menyedari bahawa asrama itu menyimpan rahsia gelap tentang sumpahan yang menghantui setiap penghuni yang tinggal di situ. Untuk menyelamatkan diri, Maya perlu membongkar misteri di sebalik kutukan tersebut sebelum terlambat.

programme.title: Arjuna EP20 S1 Ep20
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang gadis kampung naif yang datang ke bandar untuk mencari pekerjaan di sebuah pejabat dan di situ dia telah bertemu dengan bekas mat rempit yang telah jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama. Dia berusaha untuk menolong gadis itu sesuaikan diri dengan gaya hidup bandar dan akhirnya gadis kampung itu juga telah jatuh cinta kepadanya. Walaubagaimanapun kerana sifatnya yang matang, ramai wanita mencemburuinya.

programme.title: Janda Meletup
programme.desc: Rosnah, seorang janda muda cuba dipikat oleh Kamil yang tertarik dengannya namun gagal. Samad yang berasal dari Kuala Lumpur pergi ke kampung untuk mencari pembantu rumah dan bertemu Rosnah yang ingin bekerja dengannya. Kamil yang kecewa pergi ke Kuala Lumpur untuk berjumpa Rosnah selain tekadnya yang ingin bekerja dan mengahwini Rosnah. Suatu insiden terjadi menyebabkan Rosnah dan Kamil berganding bahu untuk menyelamatkan Samad.

programme.title: Tujuh Biang Keladi
programme.desc: Mona datang ke Kuala Lumpur untuk mencari pekerjaan setelah lari daripada rumah. Di Kuala Lumpur, dia tinggal serumah dengan enam orang gadis bujang dan mendapat kerja sebagai kerani. Oleh kerana memiliki raut wajah yang cantik, Mona mendapat ramai kenalan daripada orang berada yang sanggup membuat apa sahaja untuk dirinya. Pada masa yang sama, seorang murid bapa Mona yang bernama Mail telah datang mencarinya di Kuala Lumpur untuk membawanya pulang.

programme.title: Dendang Remaja
programme.desc: Di sebuah akademi seni, terdapat dua kumpulan pelajar yang berseteru. Mereka tidak serius ketika belajar dan lebih menggemari muzik dari barat. Oleh kerana tidak mendapat bimbingan yang sewajarnya, para pelajar ini menjadi semakin liar sehingga menganggu ketenteraman.

programme.title: Suara Kekasih
programme.desc: Percintaan yang ditentang keluarga kerana perbezaan darjat membuatkan Ayu dan Taufiq terpaksa membawa haluan berbeza. Ayu, penyanyi di kelab malam jatuh cinta dengan Taufiq, pengurus syarikat insuran yang berasal dari keluarga kaya. Ditentang oleh ibu Taufiq, mereka merasakan restu keluarga amat penting dan terpaksa membuat keputusan penting untuk masa depan mereka.

programme.title: Anaknya Sazali
programme.desc: Sazali tidak mahu anaknya mengamalkan pergaulan bebas sebagaimana yang pernah dilaluinya dahulu. Dia bertindak dengan mengurung anaknya Farid di dalam bilik agar tidak bercampur dengan orang lain. Tindakan itu telah membuatkan Farid menjadi seorang yang sangat pemalu dan takut untuk bergaul dengan masyarakat.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Seorang pemuda bernama Os bekerja sebagai budak pejabat di sebuah syarikat insurans di ibu kota. Pada suatu hari berlaku satu kehilangan berlian di sebuah acara pameran. Os cuba menyelesaikan kes kehilangan berlian itu dengan bantuan seekor monyet yang menjadi sahabatnya.

programme.title: Pening-Pening Lalat
programme.desc: Dino berjaya melarikan diri dari sebuah penjara dan sedang berada dalam buruan polis. Berita tentangnya mendapat liputan besar dan ditawarkan wang sebanyak RM10,000 kepada sesiapa yang menangkapnya. Mengetahui tentang itu, Dino mula menyembunyikan diri. Memutuskan untuk bersembunyi di hutan, Dino bertemu Zakaria dan Aliza.

programme.title: Tak Kisahlah Beb
programme.desc: Bob, seorang DJ di sebuah kelab malam terkenal dengan sikapnya yang suka mementikngkan diri sendiri selain perangainya yang nakal. Diperangkapnya Rozi, lalu Bob menodai dan meninggalkannya. Pertengkaran berlaku apabila mereka bertemu kembali atas apa yang Bob telah lakukan kepadanya. Setelah disedarkan rakan-rakannya, Bob menyesali tindakannya dan cuba untuk mencari jalan berbaik semula.

programme.title: Awang Spanar
programme.desc: Awang Spanar, gelaran yang diberi kerana kemahirannya yang pandai membaiki bot melalui pelbagai liku kehidupan bersama rakannya, Salleh. Percutian mereka di Kuala Lumpur bertukar menjadi sebuah pengembaraan apabila terlibat sebagai saksi kes penculikan. Sekumpulan mafia menculik anak hartawan bernama Rahim. Menjadi buruan mafia, mereka meminta bantuan seorang detektif, Lydia.

programme.title: Marah-Marah Sayang
programme.desc: Tiga jejaka yang cintakan muzik terpaksa dilepaskan dari kerja masing-masing kerana asyik leka dibuai irama ketika sedang bekerja yang menyebabkan ketidakselesaan orang lain. Rostam, Roslan dan Rosdin mula jatuh cinta terhadap tiga anak dara yang cantik namun Salina, Sarina dan Satina menolak cinta mereka. Pelbagai usaha telah dilakukan oleh mereka dan akhirnya mereka berjaya mengahwini gadis-gadis pilihan mereka itu. Syarat-syarat telah diberi jika ingin berkahwin namun telah dilanggar, ini telah mengakibatkan perkahwinan mereka menjadi kucar-kacir.

programme.desc: Rosnah, seorang janda muda cuba dipikat oleh Kamil yang tertarik dengannya namun gagal. Kamil yang kecewa pergi ke Kuala Lumpur untuk berjumpa Rosnah selain tekadnya yang ingin bekerja dan mengahwini Rosnah. Suatu insiden terjadi menyebabkan Rosnah dan Kamil berganding bahu untuk menyelamatkan Samad.

programme.desc: Dino berjaya melarikan diri dari sebuah penjara dan sedang berada dalam buruan polis. Berita tentangnya mendapat liputan besar dan ditawarkan wang sebanyak RM10,000 kepada sesiapa yang menangkapnya. Mengetahui tentang itu, Dino mula menyembunyikan diri. Memutuskan untuk bersembunyi di hutan, Dino bertemu Zakaria dan Aliza.

programme.title: Awang Spanar
programme.desc: Awang Spanar, gelaran yang diberi kerana kemahirannya yang pandai membaiki bot melalui pelbagai liku kehidupan bersama rakannya, Salleh. Percutian mereka di Kuala Lumpur bertukar menjadi sebuah pengembaraan apabila terlibat sebagai saksi kes penculikan. Sekumpulan mafia menculik anak hartawan bernama Rahim. Menjadi buruan mafia, mereka meminta bantuan seorang detektif, Lydia.

programme.title: Janda Meletup
programme.desc: Rosnah, seorang janda muda cuba dipikat oleh Kamil yang tertarik dengannya namun gagal. Samad yang berasal dari Kuala Lumpur pergi ke kampung untuk mencari pembantu rumah dan bertemu Rosnah yang ingin bekerja dengannya. Kamil yang kecewa pergi ke Kuala Lumpur untuk berjumpa Rosnah selain tekadnya yang ingin bekerja dan mengahwini Rosnah. Suatu insiden terjadi menyebabkan Rosnah dan Kamil berganding bahu untuk menyelamatkan Samad.

programme.title: Tujuh Biang Keladi
programme.desc: Mona datang ke Kuala Lumpur untuk mencari pekerjaan setelah lari daripada rumah. Di Kuala Lumpur, dia tinggal serumah dengan enam orang gadis bujang dan mendapat kerja sebagai kerani. Oleh kerana memiliki raut wajah yang cantik, Mona mendapat ramai kenalan daripada orang berada yang sanggup membuat apa sahaja untuk dirinya. Pada masa yang sama, seorang murid bapa Mona yang bernama Mail telah datang mencarinya di Kuala Lumpur untuk membawanya pulang.

programme.title: Tak Kisahlah Beb
programme.desc: Bob, seorang DJ di sebuah kelab malam terkenal dengan sikapnya yang suka mementikngkan diri sendiri selain perangainya yang nakal. Diperangkapnya Rozi, lalu Bob menodai dan meninggalkannya. Pertengkaran berlaku apabila mereka bertemu kembali atas apa yang Bob telah lakukan kepadanya. Setelah disedarkan rakan-rakannya, Bob menyesali tindakannya dan cuba untuk mencari jalan berbaik semula.

programme.title: Suara Kekasih
programme.desc: Percintaan yang ditentang keluarga kerana perbezaan darjat membuatkan Ayu dan Taufiq terpaksa membawa haluan berbeza. Ayu, penyanyi di kelab malam jatuh cinta dengan Taufiq, pengurus syarikat insuran yang berasal dari keluarga kaya. Ditentang oleh ibu Taufiq, mereka merasakan restu keluarga amat penting dan terpaksa membuat keputusan penting untuk masa depan mereka.

programme.title: Marah-Marah Sayang
programme.desc: Tiga jejaka yang cintakan muzik terpaksa dilepaskan dari kerja masing-masing kerana asyik leka dibuai irama ketika sedang bekerja yang menyebabkan ketidakselesaan orang lain. Rostam, Roslan dan Rosdin mula jatuh cinta terhadap tiga anak dara yang cantik namun Salina, Sarina dan Satina menolak cinta mereka. Pelbagai usaha telah dilakukan oleh mereka dan akhirnya mereka berjaya mengahwini gadis-gadis pilihan mereka itu. Syarat-syarat telah diberi jika ingin berkahwin namun telah dilanggar, ini telah mengakibatkan perkahwinan mereka menjadi kucar-kacir.

programme.title: Cincin Pusaka
programme.desc: Alina dan Sofian adalah dua beradik yang saling cemburu, berlumba mengalahkan satu sama lain sejak kecil. Setelah kematian nenek, mereka berebut untuk memiliki cincin pusaka nenek yang kononnya mempunyai magis tertentu. Tetapi pelbagai halangan terjadi untuk mereka mewarisinya. Mampukah mereka menghadapi segala rintangan demi sebentuk cincin pusaka?

programme.title: Nada Siar S1 Ep68
programme.desc: Sebuah program yang menyajikan kepada anda klip-klip video soundtrack yang terkandung dalam filem-filem klasik tempatan.

programme.title: Kasut Ku Kusut
programme.desc: Kasut Ku Kusut mengisahkan seorang pemuda kampung bernama Manap yang berasa kecewa kerana kasut barunya telah hilang. Sementara itu, Markos, ahli kumpulan gangster Father Dragon, ditugaskan untuk membawa Suzi kepada ketua geng. Dalam perjalanan, mereka tersesat di sebuah kampung, dan Suzi berjaya melarikan diri lalu bertemu dengan Manap yang masih mencari kasutnya. Ketika Markos menemui mereka, Manap menyedari bahawa kasut yang dipakai oleh Markos kelihatan sangat mirip dengan kasutnya yang hilang.

programme.title: Hantu Tenggek
programme.desc: Sekumpulan penipu yang diketuai oleh Tariq yang berpura-pura mengusir tempat berhantu telah diperas ugut oleh Tuan Sidek, seorang pemaju bangunan. Mereka perlu meyakinkan pesaing Tuan Sidek bahawa bangunan tertentu berhantu apabila mereka terperangkap di dalamnya. Kecuali mereka tidak perlu meyakinkan kerana bangunan itu benar-benar dihantui oleh roh yang tidak tenteram. Roh memerlukan bantuan mereka untuk memenuhi hasrat terakhirnya

programme.title: Syawal Mencari Cinta
programme.desc: Pada pagi Raya, Syawal melepak bersama rakannya dan mereka tidak menunaikan solat sunat Hari Raya. Setelah selesai solat sunat Hari Raya, dia ternampak seorang gadis yang tidak pernah dilihatnya di kampung sebelum ini. Syawal terus berkesimpulan bahawa dia telah menemui cinta sejati. Dia telah mengunjung setiap rumah di kampung untuk menjejaki gadis tersebut. Selepas sekian lama mencari tanpa membuahkan hasil, Syawal terus mengumumkan kepada seluruh kampung bahawa dia akan melaksanakan rumah terbuka untuk hari raya dan semua orang dijemput hadir ke rumahnya. Namun demikian, setelah selesai rumah terbukanya, gadis yang dicari-cari Syawal masih tidak kelihatan. Dia kecewa lalu berputus asa. Tanpa sedar, gadis yang dijejaki selama ini adalah Cinta, sepupunya sendiri.

programme.title: Hayya 2: Dream Hope And Reality
programme.desc: Filem sekuel ini menyorot trauma dan kehilangan. Hayya melarikan diri ke Indonesia lalu bertemu Lia dan Faisal, yang akhirnya menganggapnya sebagai pengikat rumah tangga mereka. Sementara Rahmat, Adhin dan Ricis terus mencarinya, rahsia keluarga Faisal terbongkar hingga tragedi besar berlaku.

programme.title: Hayya 1: The Power Of Love
programme.desc: Rahmat, wartawan yang dihantui dosa silam, berhijrah jadi relawan di kem pelarian Palestin dan bertemu Hayya, anak yatim piatu. Pertemuan itu mengubah hidupnya, namun bila dia pulang ke Indonesia untuk berkahwin dengan Yasna, tercetus konflik emosi yang rumit, lucu dan tegang antara mereka.

programme.title: Dunia Baru The Movie
programme.desc: Filem ini bermula apabila Opie menemui sepucuk surat daripada Anizah yang menyatakan bahawa dia ingin berkahwin dengan teman lelakinya, Fazley, dan telah menguburkan impiannya untuk menyambung pelajaran ke UK.

programme.title: Gerabak Cinta
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Luna, usahawan berjaya yang ditipu tunangnya, Razi. Dia kecewa apabila perniagaan yang mereka usahakan rugi kerana Razi terbabit dengan skandal wang serta mempunyai perempuan simpanan. Sementara itu, Gie pula baru saja dibuang kerja. Walaupun masih mencari kerja, dia sangat tenang dan tetap ceria. Gie reda dengan situasi menimpanya.

programme.title: Jodoh Tak Salah Alamat
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Luqman pernah mengenali seorang gadis bernama Diana ketika Diana melanggar keretanya dahulu. Diana berpenampilan seksi dan mengamalkan cara hidup barat membuatkan Luqman bersangka buruk terhadap Diana. Satu hari, Luqman ke masjid dan terserempak dengan seorang gadis cantik iaitu Adawiyah. Tanpa mengetahui, Adawiyah dan Diana adalah orang yang sama. Diana pernah terlibat dengan kemalangan dan sejak itu hidupnya berubah sepenuhnya.

programme.title: Ace Ventura: When Nature Calls
programme.desc: Selepas bersara di Tibet sebab trauma gagal selamatkan rakun, Ace Ventura (lakonan Jim Carrey) dipanggil semula sebagai penyiasat haiwan. Kali ni dia dihantar ke Afrika Timur untuk cari kelawar putih suci bernama Shikaka, yang diculik. Kalau bat species tu tak jumpa, dua suku kaum kat sana bakal berperang. Dalam pencarian penuh gila-gila ni, Ace guna gaya penyiasatan peliknya untuk selesaikan misteri.

programme.title: Qari Cilik S1 Ep15
programme.desc: Program pencarian bakat untuk menghafal al-Quran bagi kanak-kanak sehingga berusia 14 tahun.

programme.title: Merajut Gorontalo S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Separa dokumentari yang menerokai tradisi masakan Gorontalo yang pelbagai dan unik. Program ini menampilkan hidangan tradisional, cara penyediaan yang asli, dan budaya masakan tempatan di daerah Gorontalo.

programme.title: Sepenggal Doa Tulus Dari Ibu yang Merindukan Anaknya
programme.desc: Ulfa terpaksa meminjam wang daripada Adelia dan suaminya, Rudi, untuk membiayai pembedahan anaknya yang masih bayi, Vino. Ulfa berasa lega apabila pembedahan Vino berjalan lancar. Namun, hatinya hancur semula apabila Vino dibawa oleh Adelia dan Rudi mengikut perjanjian mereka. Selama bertahun-tahun, Ulfa menyimpan kerinduan terhadap anaknya dan mencari-cari keberadaan Vino. Dia sentiasa berdoa agar suatu hari nanti takdir akan mengembalikan anaknya ke pelukannya.

programme.title: D'Academy 7 S7 Ep66
programme.desc: D' Academy 7 ialah musim ketujuh rancangan nyanyian popular Indonesia yang fokus pada muzik dangdut. Peserta dari seluruh negara bertanding dengan menyanyikan lagu dangdut, menunjukkan bakat vokal dan persembahan mereka. Sepanjang musim, mereka dinilai oleh juri profesional dan undian penonton. Siapakah yang akan menjuarai D'Academy musim ketujuh?

programme.title: My Heart S1 Ep94
programme.desc: Raisa yang patah hati selepas tunangnya, Rio, hilang tiba-tiba, pergi ke Jakarta untuk mencari jawapan. Di sana, dia bertemu Mike, seorang pelakon drama popular yang sebenarnya berperwatakan sensitif dan bermasalah, berbeza dengan wataknya di kaca TV. Perkenalan mereka secara kebetulan menjadi semakin rapat apabila mereka mula mengenali diri sebenar masing-masing. Namun, cinta mereka diuji apabila terbongkar bahawa ibu Mike, Rika, adalah isteri kedua kepada ayah Raisa, menyebabkan perebutan harta antara keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Batam Bumi Segantang Lada S1 Ep8

programme.desc: Rindu dan Fauzan terpaksa berdepan dengan kenyataan pahit apabila penipuan masa lalu Rindu terbongkar. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.desc: Wu is a senior police officer has always wanted a son to carry his family name and join the force. However, he and wife are bequeathed with four daughters! As a doting father, his chief objective is to help them find happiness in their marriages. In this charming drama, Wu & his wife become their daughters greatest haven, through the ups and downs they face as married women.

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan S1 Ep5245
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation.

programme.title: Taste of Life S1 Ep257
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai Chao and his wife have five children. Having devoted his entire life to developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai sincerely hopes that one of his children will follow in his footsteps and take over the family business. However, he also respects their individual passions and aspirations. Because of their fathers dream of innovation, the lives of the Chao brothers are about to change.

However, he also respects their individual passions and aspirations. Because of their fathers dream of innovation, the lives of the Chao brothers are about to change.

programme.title: New Taiwan Go S1 Ep3316
programme.desc: Depth analysis of the day breaking news headlines to restore the truth inside.

programme.title: Stylish Man-The Chef S1 Ep3549
programme.desc: Stylish Man The Chef is co-hosted by the Golden Bell Awards winner Sam Tseng and Genie Chuo, together with professional chef, James. There are two main themes for the program, which are Big Stars Come to Cook and Five-Star Cooking Show. Stylish Man The Chef containing not only the bomb of laughter, but the audience can also gain practical cooking knowledge throughout the program.

programme.title: Stories In Taiwan S1 Ep64
programme.desc: In a playful and relaxed style, the host went deep into the corners of various towns and villages in Taiwan, looking for the uniqueness, introduced the special local customs and traditions.

programme.title: Hot Door Night S1 Ep2079
programme.desc: Different in age, generation, and hosting style, these three hosts not only can sing, act, dance, and imitate, but are also skilled in cross-talk! With this unique combination, we hope to attract viewers of all ages and spark great entertainment.

programme.title: The Sound of Happiness S1 Ep207
programme.desc: Wu is a senior police officer has always wanted a son to carry his family name and join the force. However, he and wife are bequeathed with four daughters! As a doting father, his chief objective is to help them find happiness in their marriages. In this charming drama, Wu & his wife become their daughters greatest haven, through the ups and downs they face as married women.

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan S1 Ep5246
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation.

programme.title: The Monkey King
programme.desc: After Goddess Nuwa sacrifices herself to save the mortal world, Monkey King comes into being from one of her crystals. Powerful and uncontrollable, Monkey King challenges the Jade Emperor and causes an uproar in heaven, unwittingly creating an opportunity for the wicked Buffalo Demon King to wage war in heaven.

programme.title: Protege
programme.desc: Undercover Police Nick has spent 8 years working for the drug baron Quin, so as to collect evidence of his drug trafficking activities. After gaining Quin's trust, Nick becomes his protg and succeeds him as the drug baron when Quin retires. However, Nick has lost himself in his split life between trading drugs and searching for criminal evidence.

programme.title: Bodyguards And Assassins
programme.desc: On 15 October 1906, Chinese revolutionary leader Sun Yat Sen returned to Hong Kong to stage another overthrow of the Qing dynasty. Businessman Lee and Chinese Daily's Chief Chan arrange for five bodyguards to protect Mr Sun - these are all extraordinary fighters who are ready and up for fierce battles against the Qing assassination army.

programme.title: I Fine Thank You Love You
programme.desc: Pleng, an English tutor, helps her student to pass a break up message in English to her boyfriend Gym. Gym knows nothing about English but wants to win back his girlfriend from the US, so he asks Pleng to teach him. Boorish and a slow learner, Gym makes many hilarious mistakes when learning English and ends up falling for Pleng.

programme.title: The Grey Men 2
programme.desc: Triad boss Song seeks to whitewash his image and seize Laika's mayoral seat amid a regime change. He faces a funding shortfall despite colluding with officials, and gets his right-hand man and enforcer to commit crimes to boost his funds and power. Just as Song believes success is imminent, the dynamics between the three take an unexpected turn

programme.title: Where The Wind Blows
programme.desc: Founded in the 70s, Hong Kong's ICAC is committed to fight corruption in the police force. Detectives Lui Lok and Nam Kong build a corruption system that creates conflicts between the triad and the police. When ICAC hunts down the two, their control finally comes to an end. Where the wind blows, Hong Kong is no longer what it used to be!

programme.title: No One Like Me
programme.desc: Yang Qian Huan, the third disciple of the Imperial Astronomer, was once a golden boy. However, since the birth of Xu Qi An, his glory has waned. His relentless pursuit cannot defy a merciless truth: all has been foretold. Yet rising from his downfall, Yang defiantly forges his own path, refusing to bow to fate.

programme.title: Love at First Lie
programme.desc: An ordinary, cheerful and kind-hearted girl Bao, meets a troubled rich guy Edward by chance one summer. To ruin his father's remarriage plans, Edward hires Bao and her friend to sabotage the wedding and that is how Bao and Edward meet and fall in love. All seems well for the sweet couple until their love quickly takes an unexpected turn

programme.title: Imprisoned 2: There Is No Escape From Fate
programme.desc: Hong Kong businessman Yu and his secretary travel abroad for business meetings. When the secretary is killed in their hotel, Yu is arrested. Despite pleading not guilty, Yu is imprisoned in a cruel multinational prison where the warden enjoys torturing prisoners, and he must find a way to escape from this dark and deadly prison to survive.

programme.title: Kungfu Stuntmen
programme.desc: Hong Kong action cinema is famous for its real kung fu moves performed by a group called Kung Fu Stuntmen. This docu-film pays tribute to the generations of kung fu stuntmen, with the crew spending over two years digging archives and interviewing many talents, including the most prominent masters like Jackie Chan, Donnie Yen and Sammo Hung.

programme.title: Kung Fu Dunk
programme.desc: Shi Jie grew up in a martial arts school and possesses an extraordinary shooting skill. Street hustler Chen Li sees his talent and arranges for him to join a university basketball team. With his kung fu dunking skill, Shi Jie manages to win all college basketball matches, bringing him wealth and also strengthening his relationship with Chen Li.

programme.title: CZ12
programme.desc: Hawk leads a mercenary team to recover the bronze heads of the 12 Chinese zodiac animals, which were looted by foreigners in the 1800s. With a promise of a 10 times bonus by MP Corp if he can recover all of them, Hawk stops at nothing to accomplish the mission.

programme.title: Customs Frontline
programme.desc: After boarding an unauthorized cargo ship and finding its entire crew dead, the Hong Kong Customs officers uncover a hidden cache of illegal weapons linked to an international conflict. As Customs officer Zhou Zheng Li and Interpol's Ying go undercover, they unveil a multinational operation with ties closer to home.

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Eva's mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mother's wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Eva's heart?

programme.title: The Wandering Earth II
programme.desc: In this prequel, humans build enormous engines on the Earth's surface to find a new home when the sun is burning out. In the dangerous universe, a group of young people has to step forward once again to fight in the critical battle to save the Earth.

programme.title: Wish Comes True
programme.desc: Xiao Fei is a cheerful girl who has been abandoned by her mother. One day, she encounters a gifted young man named Zi Wai, who is battling a rare disease. Determined to help him, she embarks on a journey to find his lost love. Even when they discover that the drug treating Wai is ineffective, they choose to embrace hope and love together.

programme.title: The Ex-files 4: Marriage Plan
programme.desc: Two brothers, Meng Yun and Yu Fei, are of marriageable age and are facing challenges in love. Yun dodges family pressure to marry after his breakup, while Fei and his girlfriend opt for a marriage cooling-off period to tackle marriage issues.

programme.title: Project Gutenberg
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police hunts for a counterfeiting gang led by a mastermind known as Painter. The gang is so skillful that it's almost impossible to distinguish between its counterfeit currency and real money. In an effort to find Painter's real identity, the Police recruits artist Lee Man to assist in solving the case.

programme.title: God Of Gamblers 2
programme.desc: A new chapter of the highly successful "God of Gamblers". The legend's disciple Andy Lau is now rising in the gambling world as the "Knight of Gamblers", clashing with another gambling icon, the wild psychic Stephen Chow (aka "Saint of Gamblers") who wants to follow the God. They mix like oil and water in a series of tricks and mishaps, but are forced to join hands against their master's nemesis on the gambling table.

programme.title: All U Need Is Love
programme.desc: Ten major film companies join forces on a comedy-drama film to raise funds and create jobs for industry workers during the COVID-19 pandemic. This film features an all-star ensemble cast starring for free, with the story revolving around a group of hotel guests placed under quarantine in Hong Kong.

programme.title: Bounty Hunters
programme.desc: A group of bounty hunters, including San, Yo, Cat, Swan and Bobo, are tasked to track down the culprit of a series of bombings that have plagued an international hotel group. Unfortunately, Swan, Cat and Bobo are kidnapped by the mastermind of the bombings. Can San and Yo save them? Will the bounty hunters accomplish their mission?

programme.title: Lucky Star 2015
programme.desc: When a talent manager meets a guy whose voice resembles the famous comedian Stephen Chow, things starts to stir up in the show biz. "Lucky Star 2015" is a hilarious comedy starring actors from both Hong Kong and Taiwan, including Eric Tsang, Dada Chan and Wong Cho Lam.

programme.title: From Beijing With Love
programme.desc: Stephen Chow writes, directs & stars in this hilarious James Bond spoof that sees the Chinese government assign their worst secret agent (Chow) to recover a stolen dinosaur skull.

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: L Storm
programme.desc: ICAC Chief Officer Luk and Chief Inspector Lau both hit a dead end when investigating their respective bribery and money laundering cases. When Luk is accused of bribery after being framed by the money launderers, he risks everything he has to find crucial evidence against them to clear his name.

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: Raging Fire
programme.desc: As the police sets to arrest a drug lord, a team of masked thugs steals the drugs and murders the cops. Inspector Bong is devastated to see the aftermath of the carnage and soon discovers that the killers are led by Ngo, a former fellow cop who was forced into a life of crime by him. As the two men meet again, it is time to settle the score

programme.title: Ready O/R Knot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi have been together for five years since they first met in a wedding banquet, but marriage soon becomes a challenge to their relationship. Heidi sees marriage as a testimony of their love, while Guy sees it as doomsday. Can the couple resolve their conflict? Are they ready or not?

programme.title: No One Like Me
programme.desc: Yang Qian Huan, the third disciple of the Imperial Astronomer, was once a golden boy. However, since the birth of Xu Qi An, his glory has waned. His relentless pursuit cannot defy a merciless truth: all has been foretold. Yet rising from his downfall, Yang defiantly forges his own path, refusing to bow to fate.

programme.title: Stuntman
programme.desc: Washed-up stunt director Li Sen is offered the role of action choreographer on his director friend's final film. Bringing along an ambitious young stuntman, the two generations risk everything to stage a comeback. As Li Sen battles his fierce temper and past mistakes, he also strives to mend his relationship with his estranged daughter.

programme.title: One More Chance
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as a down-on-his-luck gambler, Water, whose ex-girlfriend asked him to take care of their autistic son. As Water lives with his son, he soon finds his goal in life. When he discovers his son's talent in running, Water decides to give up his dissipated life and support his son to achieve his dream.

programme.title: The Mirror and the Lichee
programme.desc: The curious title in this Huangmei Opera romance refers to the two props that signal a happy beginning between a scholar and a local beauty. The scholar polishes mirrors so as to be closer to his love, who signals her approval by tossing him some lichees. From that point on the course of their love becomes rocky, complete with murder and suicide.

programme.title: The Delightful Forest
programme.desc: The legendary hero Wu Sung is sent to a prison in Meng province after murdering his adulterous sister-in-law and her lover. While in prison, the officer Shih En spares Wu the humiliating baton punishment. Owing Shih a favour, Wu decides to help Shih get his restaurant back at all costs when it was forcefully taken over by a local thug.

programme.title: Two Con Men
programme.desc: Two Con Men is a wonderfully twisted, pseudo-romantic comedy in the vein of "Robin Hood" meets "The Sting". Starring Liang Tien as Clever Chan and Chang Ying (who's done over 400 films) as Tricky Ching, it's the age-old competition between a rookie con artist versus the ultimate, experienced flimflam man. It's a game Chen cannot afford to lose, because people's lives - including his own, hang in the balance of good versus evil.

programme.title: The Avenging Eagle
programme.desc: Qi Ming Xing, an assassin of the Iron Boat Clan, decides to quit the clan. When hunted by the clan, he is saved by Swordsman Zhuo Yi Fan. Zhuo accidentally discovers that Qi is the killer of his wife, but forgives him after knowing Qi's guilt over her death. The two finally team up to destroy the evil clan.

programme.title: Pale Passion
programme.desc: Fa is an obsessive man who loves his wife Ah Hsia but is easily jealous and abuses her. When she leaves him one day, Fa hooks up with another woman, Hsing. A deadly triangle develops when Fa runs into Ah Hsia again and decides to win her back

programme.title: Invincible Shaolin
programme.desc: An evil Qing general comes up with a plan to rid the Shaolin masters once and for all. He invites three Northern Shaolin experts to fight against three Southern Shaolin disciples. After the contest, the general secretly kills the Southerners and places the blame on the Northerners. This leads to in-fighting between both Shaolin schools.

programme.title: Double Bliss
programme.desc: Dong and Chu plan to get married but their families who are lifelong rivals, disapproved. They decide to fake suicide and eventually get both of their parents to settle their differences and approve the marriage. Concurrently, a record company announces that they will release Dong's songs, leading to double bliss for the couple.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: Threatened by the Yuan who are closing in to rule the whole of China, a band of Song survivors band together to save their prime minister. This bold and fearless heroes fighting for their cause are led by international star, Lo Lieh (Glass Tears, Killer Clans) and Shi Szu (Lovers Destiny), who must fight their way out of trap after trap. But they can't escape them all, and eventually the two end up in prison... it is either death or a fight to the end!

programme.title: Call of the Sea
programme.desc: A young fisherman, Chin Hu is in love with his childhood friend Hsiao Yu. However, the only son of a town bully lusts after Hsiao Yu's beauty and tries all possible ways to approach her. Chin Hu protects another woman from the bully one day, leading Hsiao Yu to misunderstand him and suspect that they are having an affair...

programme.title: Men From The Monastery
programme.desc: At the end of the Ming Dynasty, Wu San Gui betrays his people to the Qing officials and recruits fighters from all backgrounds. Members from Wudan and Ermei are the first to yield and collude with local bullies. When they start attacking the Shaolin Monastery, its most famous disciples have to band together and fight against the enemies.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre 2
programme.desc: Only by bringing together the powerful Heaven Sword and the mighty Dragon Sabre can six martial arts sects struggling for supremacy be saved in this thrilling sequel to Chu Yuan's original hit.

programme.title: The Shepherd Girl
programme.desc: In this musical drama, Hsiu Hsiu, a beautiful shepherd girl, falls in love with a handsome boatman Ta Lung. However, she cannot afford to marry him because of her father's towering debt from gambling. To complicate the matter, a rival suitor promises to pay off all her father's debts on one condition: that Hsiu Hsiu marries him...

programme.title: Asia-pol
programme.desc: Asiapol agent Yang Ming Xuan trails a shipment of contraband gold being delivered to gang leader, George Eaton. He enlists the help of a Chinese woman who is trying to avenge her sister and narrowly escapes several deadly traps as he closes in on Eaton's location. This spy film is loosely inspired by the James Bond movies.

programme.title: Little Hero
programme.desc: An orphan, Little Bastard is taken on and trained as a fighter by a hermit. When Little Bastard grows up, he feels he is old enough to go out and look for his parents. Luckily for him, he befriends a beggar, Hsiao Yi, who being street-wise, manages to help him find his family, but somehow gets into trouble with the gang.

programme.title: Secret Service of the Imperial Court
programme.desc: Zhao Bu Fan is the sergeant of the government's secret police. Wang is a cruel and ruthless eunuch who takes over the Emperor's ruling power and leads the team of secret agents. After witnessing the atrocities committed by Eunuch Wang, Sergeant Zhao decides to defect but ends up being hunted by his friends, comrades and even his father.

programme.title: Flying Guillotine 2
programme.desc: In a time of anti-Manchu sentiment, Emperor Yong Zheng employs his ruthless Blood Hound Corps to silence any dissenters. Only one man and his signature weapon, The Flying Guillotine, stand in their way.

programme.title: Crazy Shaolin Disciples
programme.desc: The story revolves around three lay disciples of the Shaolin Temple: Fang Shi Yu, Hong Xi Guan, and Hu Hui Qian. Monk Jie instructs them in martial arts, but their frequent competitions with fellow disciple Wu Qing spark rivalries. The once serene Shaolin Temple is plunged into chaos, yet even the abbot cannot help but be amused by their antics.

programme.title: Heroes Two
programme.desc: Shaolin disciple Hong escapes from the burning temple after it is attacked by the Qing army and is badly wounded. He is handed over to the Qing soldiers by Fang as he mistakes Hong for a bandit. When Fang realizes his mistakes, he tries all ways to help Hong escape so that they can team up to fight the Qing army together.

programme.title: Passing Flickers
programme.desc: This film is an amusing insider's look at the Hong Kong film industry and is based on Director Li Han Hsiang's popular newspaper column recounting his work at Shaw Brothers. The collection of some of his funniest and most surreal film musings of the era, filled with behind-the-scene asides, this is a must-see for any Hong Kong cinema aficionado!

programme.title: The Trail of the Broken Blade
programme.desc: After avenging his father's death by assassinating a high official, Li Yue disappears into hiding as a fugitive. His fiance enlists a swordsmanwho secretly loves herto search for him, unaware that the bandit Xiao Mei has also fallen for Li Yue. Their intertwined love quadrangle explores themes of sacrifice, devotion and selfless love.

programme.title: Return Of The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This sequel makes for more bittersweet laughs and heart-wrenching misfortune, as Ah Niu gets out of the jail to find his true love becoming the wife of an abusive husband, and his uncle further exploits his naive nature.

programme.title: The Brave Archer 2
programme.desc: Knowing Guo Jing has won Huang Rong's hand in marriage using the kung fu learned from Jiu Yin manual, Ouyang Feng captures Huang and agrees to release her only if Guo can dictate the content of the manual. Will Guo give in to the threat?

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: Les Belles
programme.desc: Acknowledged as one of the greatest Hong Kong musicals, this lavish movie starring Linda Lin, who won Best Actress for her performance, infuses its wispy plot with style and wit, and the results are pure pleasure.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung goes incognito to mix with his people and understand their needs. He encounters many strange things along the way, including being arrested and nearly beheaded. Who will save him?

programme.title: King Gambler
programme.desc: This film was actually a lively forerunner to the gambling film craze, which eventually swept Asian cinema. Here, it's cardsharp versus cardsharp with a lot more kung-fu action, in a battle of wits and fists to become the king of the casino. The double stings and triple crosses raise in complexity and imagination until what started as an unusual box office risk became a top ten hit of 1976.

programme.title: Madam White Snake
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai is perfect as Pak Su-cheng, the stunning snake goddess who assumes a womanly form so that she can taste the pleasures of a human life! Pak seduces young scholar, Hsu Hsien when she recognises him as her saviour in another life 1,000 years ago. But when Buddhist monk Fa Hai finds out about the union, the pair is forced to split...

programme.title: Bat Without Wings
programme.desc: The Bat Without Wings, a notorious rapist-murderer, has returned after a five-year absence. A young swordsman and a convoy master investigate the case and suspect that the Bat may be framed. A saying goes that a treasure map is hidden under the Bat's knife, so they try to use that to hunt the real culprit

programme.title: The Dream Of The Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the great Chinese classic novel of the same name, the son of renowned Jia family, Bao Yu, is deeply in love with his cousin, Dai Yu. However, his mother disapproves of their relationship and plots to arrange Bao Yu to marry another rich girl, resulting in a tragic ending for the perfect couple.

programme.title: The Magnificent Trio
programme.desc: A group of farmers who are being oppressed by the local magistrates kidnap one of the magistrate's daughter in the hope of being heard by the authorities. A wandering swordsman offers his help and aiding him are two fighters who have both switched sides from being the oppressors to the oppressed. The trio fight back against the magistrates!

programme.title: The 5 Billion Dollar Legacy
programme.desc: A crippled billionaire mails a letter to each of his long-lost daughters inviting them to go to Japan, in the hope that he will find a worthy heir to inherit his vast fortune. The sisters finally meet abroad the plane to Japan, and one of them is taken with a man who is going to investigate the death of his lawyer uncle in a mysterious hit-and-run.

programme.title: Shaolin Intruders
programme.desc: On a routine courier mission, the prestigious Chief was murdered by four mysterious monks. When all evidence pointed to Ching Hua, his friend Lei decides to clear his name by barging in the Shaolin Temple thrice. When Lei thought justice was served for the culprits, he soon realizes the table had turned and the monks stroke again. What follows is a series of intense pursuit for the ultimate villain!

programme.title: The Lotus Lamp
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai plays both mother and son in this lavish fable about a goddess who falls in love with a mortal scholar (Cheng Pei-pei in her debut role). Over two years in production, it was released on the first anniversary of Linda's tragic suicide.
